creator: Indigo Ag
descriptionHtml:
Market your grain.
Minimize risk.
Maximize profit.

Get a jump on the market. Control every step of the grain sale process with access to experts when you need it.


Personalized bids for your farm.
Commodity & specialty bids, locally & further afield, priced for your location.

Take control with offers.
Set your own price by casting an offer into the market. Throw a wider net.

Set and forget notifications
Get notified about hot bids, negotiations and your offers.

Manage market risk.
Work with our experts to achieve your pricing goals.

Hassle-free freight
Hot bid too far away? Access competitive freight at the touch of a button.

Negotiate a fair deal
Market not beating your breakeven? Negotiate any bid with just a few taps.

Incoming hot bids
Access to exclusive posted and non-posted bids from our buyer partners across many markets
descriptionShort: Market your grain. Minimize risk. Maximize profit.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We update Indigo Marketplace regularly to bring you all our latest features, bug fixes and performance improvements.
In this release:
View basis bids as their cash equivalent price with the addition of futures prices in the bid list and bid details
